# Theme tokens (`src/styles.scss` + `src/styles/_interaction.scss`)

Portal and shared UI use a **4-layer surface stack** mirrored semantically in light and dark. Do not hardcode hex in component SCSS тАФ use CSS variables from `styles.scss`. Do not reintroduce flat dark chrome or translucent card backgrounds.

## Surface layers

| Layer | Token | Light | Dark | Used by |
|-------|-------|-------|------|---------|
| Chrome | `--bg-chrome` | `#ffffff` | `#0b0f19` | sidebar, topbar |
| Canvas | `--bg-app` | `#f1f5f9` | `#0d1220` | body, portal scroll area, hub tab sticky bg |
| Surface | `--bg-surface` | `#ffffff` | `#151c2e` | cards, table shell, form sections, dialogs |
| Inset | `--bg-inset` | `#f8fafc` | `#111827` | chips band, table header row |
| Control | `--bg-control` | `#ffffff` | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | inputs, filter search/buttons, form fields |

**Aliases** (prefer semantic tokens in new code; aliases exist for backward compat):

- `--bg-sidebar`, `--bg-topbar` тЖТ `--bg-chrome`
- `--bg-form-card`, `--bg-table-card`, `--bg-confirm-dialog`, `--bg-table-filter-panel` тЖТ `--bg-surface`
- `--bg-form-input`, `--bg-table-control` тЖТ `--bg-control`
- `--bg-table-filter-toolbar` тЖТ `--bg-surface`
- `--bg-table-filter-chips`, `--bg-table-header` тЖТ `--bg-inset`

**Card emphasis (both themes):** surfaces contrast with canvas. In light, surface equals chrome; in dark, surface is intentionally lighter than chrome/canvas.

**Elevation:** light surfaces may use `--shadow-surface` (`0 1px 3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.06)`); dark uses border + color step only (`--shadow-surface: none`).

## Table chrome (split card тАФ default)

`DataTableComponent` default `tableChromeVariant` is `'splitCard'`. Layout global styles: `src/styles/_table-chrome-split-card.scss`.

```text
Canvas (--bg-app) visible between cards
  тФЬтФА Controls card (--bg-surface) тАФ toolbar (--bg-surface) + chips band (--bg-inset)
  тФВ    тФЬтФА Toolbar: search + view toggle (desktop: LayoutGrid/List) + Filters toggle (Funnel; desktop: label; mobile: icon-only + active dot)
  тФВ    тФФтФА Chips band (desktop: chips + Clear top-right; mobile: Clear row then full-width compact chips)
  тФВ    тФФтФА Control inputs (--bg-control)
  тФФтФА Data card (--bg-surface)
       тФФтФА List view: sticky table header (--bg-inset) + rows (--bg-table-row-hover)
       тФФтФА Card view (desktop): responsive grid (2 cols; 3 cols тЙе1100px) тАФ styles in `_table-chrome-split-card.scss` under `data-table--card-view`
```

**Desktop card grid:** global styles on `app-data-table.data-table--card-view .data-table-cards--grid` (not component SCSS тАФ avoids `display: flex` override). `padding-top: 0.75rem` above first card row; `gap: 1rem` between cards.

**Table row cards (card view тАФ mobile + desktop toggle):** `--border-table-row-card`, `--shadow-table-row-card`, `--shadow-table-row-card-hover` in `styles.scss`; chrome in `_table-chrome-split-card.scss` (`0.75rem` radius, `1.125rem` padding, subtle elevation). Flat data shell, `1rem` gap, stacked fields, entity spine per row when `entityTab` is set. Hover lifts border + shadow on clickable rows.

**Active filters (split card):** neutral `3px` left on `.data-table-controls-card--active` when no `entityTab`. Entity hosts: **3px left + 1px top** on controls card; **list** view data card keeps spine; **card** view data card is flat тАФ filter state via chips/active count/dot, not border upgrade. Inner `.data-table-filters--active` must **not** add its own `border-left`. See `table-filters.mdc`.

**User hub tables:** when `entityTab` is set, controls card keeps entity spine; **card view** (mobile + desktop toggle) uses flat data shell with spine per row card; **list** view data card keeps full spine. No chips wash, no filter-active border emphasis. See `entity-service-colors.mdc`.

**Table header tokens:** `--border-table-header-strong`, `--shadow-table-header-sticky`, `--text-table-header-size` (caption), `--text-table-header-weight` (semibold).

## Status workflow tokens

`--status-*` in `styles.scss` тАФ **workflow pills only** (`StatusBadgeComponent`). Not entity service colors (`--entity-*`).

| Status | Hue family | Tokens |
|--------|------------|--------|
| `open` | Green | `--status-open-bg`, `--status-open-text` |
| `in_progress` | Blue | `--status-in-progress-bg`, `--status-in-progress-text` |
| `canceled` | Red | `--status-canceled-bg`, `--status-canceled-text` |
| `closed` | Amber | `--status-closed-bg`, `--status-closed-text` |

Light theme mixes base hue 14% with `#ffffff`; dark theme mixes 22% with `transparent`. Full hex table: `entity-status.mdc`.

Search input focus: `--border-form-input-focus` (not `--text-muted`).

**Legacy variant:** `'bandLadder'` тАФ single `.data-table-card` with three bands; styles in `src/styles/_table-chrome-band-ladder.scss`.

## Typography scale

Defined in `:root` / theme blocks тАФ use instead of hardcoded `font-size` / `font-weight` in shared UI:

| Token | Value | Typical use |
|-------|-------|-------------|
| `--font-size-page-title` | `1.5rem` (`--font-size-page-title-mobile`: `1.25rem`) | `PageTitleComponent` h1 |
| `--font-size-section-title` | `1.125rem` (`--font-size-section-title-mobile`: `1rem`) | form section h2, dialog title |
| `--font-size-card-title` | `1rem` | intent card, metric card title |
| `--font-size-body` | `0.875rem` | body, subtitles, buttons, tabs |
| `--font-size-body-sm` | `0.8125rem` | hints, back link, filter controls |
| `--font-size-caption` | `0.75rem` | status badges, filter active count |
| `--font-weight-regular` тАж `--font-weight-bold` | 400тАУ700 | semantic weights |
| `--line-height-tight` / `snug` / `normal` | 1.2 / 1.35 / 1.5 | |
| `--letter-spacing-tight` / `--letter-spacing-overline` | page titles / uppercase labels |

**Text roles:**

- `--text-primary` тАФ headings, body
- `--text-muted` тАФ subtitles, helpers
- `--text-secondary` тАФ alias of `--text-muted`; default state for text links
- `--table-cell-primary-color` тАФ always `var(--text-primary)` (no separate dark body color)

## Interaction tokens

In `styles.scss`:

- `--transition-fast: 0.15s ease`
- `--border-hover: var(--text-muted)`
- `--bg-hover-subtle: var(--bg-active)`
- `--bg-hover-row: var(--bg-table-row-hover)`
- `--bg-primary-hover` тАФ `color-mix` on `--bg-form-btn-primary` per theme (not opacity)
- `--shadow-hover-surface: var(--shadow-table-actions-menu)`

Mixins in `src/styles/_interaction.scss` тАФ `@use 'styles/interaction' as interaction;`:

| Mixin | Use for |
|-------|---------|
| `interactive-surface` | Clickable cards with border + shadow hover; **no `translateY` lift** |
| `interactive-text-link` | Text links тАФ `--text-secondary` тЖТ `--text-primary` + underline on hover/focus |
| `interactive-control` | Tabs, filter buttons, outlined controls тАФ `--bg-hover-subtle` fill |
| `interactive-primary-btn` | Primary CTAs тАФ `--bg-primary-hover` (not `opacity: 0.92`) |
| `focus-ring-neutral` | Portal focus rings тАФ `outline: 2px solid var(--text-muted)`; **not `--portal-accent`** on portal content |

**Hover rules (do not regress):**

1. No `translateY` / card lift on portal content cards.
2. No opacity-only primary button hover тАФ use `--bg-primary-hover`.
3. Secondary buttons: `--bg-hover-row` or `--bg-hover-subtle`.
4. Text links: color shift + underline (never opacity alone).
5. Table rows / mobile cards: `--bg-table-row-hover`.
6. Portal page content: neutral focus rings and hovers тАФ `--portal-accent` is **guest picker / login / register only** (see `layout.mdc`).

